      "span_text": "A total of 41 probands who had bilateral hearing loss and lacked the known mutations in common deafness genes, including GJB2, SLCA26A4 and m.1555A>G in MT-RNR1  , were recruited from Chang Gung Memorial Hospital (CGMH)."
